window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Cultivate the energetic power of magic with renowned witch Silver RavenWolf.</p> <p><i>The Witching Hour </i>shows you how to use the right tools, materials, and techniques for powders and spells that work. Explore the secrets of fluid condensers, beeswax, and the planets. Create your own conjuring bags and sachets. Discover how to work with powders, herbs, and magical timing with more than 100 recipes and formulas for a variety of purposes. Awaken the depths of your personal power and perform your magic with courage and confidence. This book shows you how to transform yourself and your world with the application of essential skills and true intent.</p>"; 
